---
title: Pork & Parmesan Meatballs with Apple Relish & Roasted Potatoes
description: We love this meal – full of twists on the classic meat and veg. Pork mince is a great base for big bold flavours and with Parmesan and rustic herbs partnering up, you can banish memories of boring meatballs forever.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-and-parmesan-meatballs-f2f81fc0.jpg
